author: Reuters Editorial
title: RPT-India To Consolidate 35 Overseas State-Run Bank Branches-Finmin
text:
(Repeats to wider subscribers with no changes to text)
March 1 (Reuters) -
* INDIA’S FINMIN SAYS TO“CONSOLIDATE” 35 OVERSEAS BANK BRANCHES, 69 MORE UNDER REVIEW
* INDIA’S FINMIN SAYS GOVERNMENT TO EXAMINE ALL STATE-RUN BANK OVERSEAS OPERATIONS; NON-VIABLE OPERATIONS ABROAD TO BE SHUT TO CUT COSTS
* INDIA’S FINMIN SAYS GOVERNMENT TO CONSOLIDATE EQUITY STAKE IN JOINT VENTURES HAVING MULTIPLE STATE-RUN BANK PARTNERS Source text for Eikon: [ ] (Reporting By Malini Menon)
